- Extract to /usr/local/
- Install dependencies: sudo apt-get install autoconf automake bison flex gcc libmpfr-dev libncurses5-dev libreadline-dev libusb-dev make patch subversion texinfo wget
- Link missing file: sudo ln -s /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libmpfr.so.6 /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libmpfr.so.4
- Install sign_np to /usr/local/pspdev/bin
